---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { User, Folder, Mail, Linkedin, Github, FileText, Feather } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Sidebar -->
  <div slot="sidebar">
    <aside class="w-48 bg-[#262626] fixed top-0 left-0 h-full flex flex-col py-6 gap-4 px-3">
      <button class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-zinc-700 bg-zinc-700">
        <User className="w-6 h-6 text-zinc-400" />
        <span class="text-sm">About</span>
      </button>
      <button class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-zinc-700">
        <Folder className="w-6 h-6 text-zinc-400" />
        <span class="text-sm">Projects</span>
      </button>
      <button class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-zinc-700">
        <Mail className="w-6 h-6 text-zinc-400" />
        <span class="text-sm">Contact</span>
      </button>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <!-- Main content -->
  <main class="ml-48 bg-[#171716] min-h-screen text-white relative">
    <!-- Background banner -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[380px] bg-cover bg-center border-b border-zinc-700" style="background-image: url('/bg.jpg'); z-index: 0;"></div>

    <div class="px-8 pt-[18rem] pb-10 relative z-10">
      <!-- Profile Card Container -->
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-[#171716]/90 backdrop-blur-md border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
        <img
          src="/profile-placeholder.jpg"
          alt="Profile"
          class="w-56 rounded-full border-2 border-zinc-700 mx-auto -mt-36 object-cover aspect-square shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]"
        />
        <p class="text-zinc-300 mt-4 text-lg">Hello, my name is</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold mt-1 mb-1">firstName lastName</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base">Career</p>

        <!-- Buttons -->
        <div class="mt-5 flex justify-center gap-3">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-600 px-6 py-2 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white hover:text-black">
            <Linkedin className="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-300 hover:text-black" />
            <span class="font-medium">LinkedIn</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.github.com" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-600 px-6 py-2 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white hover:text-black">
            <Github className="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-300 hover:text-black" />
            <span class="font-medium">GitHub</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-600 px-6 py-2 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white hover:text-black">
            <FileText className="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-300 hover:text-black" />
            <span class="font-medium">Resume</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="mt-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <Feather className="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-400" /> Introduction
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque at velit nec nunc efficitur sodales. Sed facilisis dignissim tellus non congue. Proin tristique imperdiet lacus, sed tristique justo gravida a. In ut justo nec arcu suscipit porta a ut purus. Suspendisse congue ex at luctus pretium. Vivamus tempor libero sit amet lectus pretium convallis. Ut eget sapien velit. Aenean sed facilisis erat.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
